text:
Ro: Hey guys, it’s Ro! I’m here with my
sister Mo today.
Mo: Hey everyone!

Ro: We asked you guys which game we should
play next, and we got so many requests for…
Mo: The Oreo Challenge!

Mo: I was so excited I even put on my Oreo
shirt today!
Ro: Yeah, Mo’s dressed as an Oreo.

Ro: For those of you who have never played
the Oreo challenge, it’s very easy!

Ro: The both of us are going to be blindfolded
and we’re going to be tasting 10

Ro: different Oreos and guessing what they
are.

Mo: Alright, I think we’re ready so let’s
get started and put our blindfolds on.
Ro: Alright, doo-doo, doo-doo, doo-doo!

Mo: These really awesome aviator blindfolds.
Ro: Oh yeah!
Ro: Bring the cookies!
Mo: 1st cookie! Let’s try it out!

Ro: Are you ready? Mo: Yeah, ready? Ro: Take
a bite.
Mo: Mmm! Ro: Mmmmmm! Mmmmmm!

Ro: We’re gonna call it on 3, ready? 1,
2, 3…
Both: MINT!

Mo: Oh yeah, these are good! Ro: We did it!
Mo: These are so good!

Ro: That’s it! Point for both of us! Mo:
Mmmhmm!
Ro: Ding, ding!

Mo: Gotta pace myself, we have, uh, 9 more
Oreos to go!
Ro: I don’t! I’m a cookie monster!

Ro: Round 2, we’re off to a good start,
let’s do this!
Mo: OK, OK you ready? Ro: Uh-huh.

Mo: It’s really sweet, do you know what
it is? Ro: No! Ahahaha!
Ro: Caramel! Mo: Watermelon!

Mo: OK, let’s check… Ro: What was it?
Mo: Those are way off!
Both: Lemon?
Mo: Oh, that makes more sense!
Mo: Alright, 3rd cookie, here we go.
Mo: OK, ready? Ro: OK.
Mo: I don’t know…
Mo: 1, Both: 2, 3…
Mo: Gingerbread. Ro: Coffee.
Mo: OK ready? Let’s look… What is…

Mo: Birthday cake? Ro: Birthday cake? Mo:
What?

Ro: Last one was a bust but now we’re onto the
4th cookie, I have a good feeling.

Mo: Alright! Ro: Alright, you ready to try
something new? Mo: Yeah, here we go.

Ro: Oh, what is this? Mo: What? Ro: Is this
an Oreo? Is this an Oreo?

Mo: I… I don’t know. Let’s try it. Ro:
OK.
Mo: OK, I have a guess. Ro: OK, 1, 2, 3…
Mo: S’more Oreo! Ro: Coconut!

Ro: Coconut! Oh point, point, point, point!
Mo: They’re coconut delight, OK.

Ro: Oh yeah, oh yeah, oh yeah! I only got
that because, Molly, um, I know my coconuts.
Ro: ‘cuz I like piña coladas!

Mo: Alright, so it’s round 5 and it’s time
for me to catch up!
Mo: Ready?
Ro: Mpppppt!
Mo: I think I, I think I know this one. Ro: Me too! Mo: OK, you ready? Ro: OK ready!
Both: Original!
Mo: Yup! Ro: Yesss!!!! Mo: Nailed it!

Both: Ready! Ro: Cuz I’m.. Always ready!
Mo: What are you doing?
Ro: For Oreos, for Oreos, for… Molly?

Ro: Let’s try this! Mo: Alright, here we
go.
Ro: Got my cookie! Mo: Oh pfft! Stop!
Ro: Mmmmmm! Ha-ha-ha!
Mo: Oh hm-hm-hm-hm-hm-hm!

Both: Mmmmm! Ro: This is like a fruit or something.
Mo: Mmmhmm!
Ro: Grape! Mo: Strawberry!
Ro: Berry… Mo: Oh berry!

Mo: Well hey, there’s a… There’s a strawberry
on the front so… So that counts!

Mo: That counts! Ro: Yeah, that counts. Strawberry
is a berry.

Mo: Woo-hoo! Ro: Is a grape a berry? Does
that count? Mo: No…

Mo: That means we’re 3-3 we’re tied again!
Ro: Huuuuuh!

Ro: We’re tied? Mo: I’m catching up! Dun-dun-dun!
Ro: Show down!
Mo: Haha! I love this! Hahahahaha!
Mo: Tie game, here’s round 7!

Ro: Oh they’re little! Mo: Oh, they’re
babies! Ro: Baby flavor!
Ro: Mmmmmmmmm! Mo: Mmmhmm!
Both: Peanut Butter!
Ro: Ohhhh! Reese’s! Mo: Ohhh these!

Ro: They’re Reese’s flavored, so peanut
butter, that’s correct. Mo: Yeah!
Mo: We should both get a point for that one.
Ro: Hold on, just second… OK, settle, settle
Ro: A-hahahahaha!
Mo: OK, ready?
Mo: Hmmmm… Ro: Om, yum, yum, yum!
Ro: OK, ready? Mo: Mmmhmm.
Ro: Cinnamon! Mo: Gingerbread!

Mo: Pffft! We weren’t… Ro: Pumpkin Spice?
Mo: We… we were both wrong on that one.

Ro: Oh look! There’s little cinnamon sticks
on the front,

Ro: so… I’m gonna take 1/2 a point. What
do you think about that?
Mo: I’ll give it to you. Ro: OK, 4 and 1/2.

Mo: Alright, round 9, let’s see how this
one goes!

Mo: What do you think? Uh-oh, uh-oh, uh-oh
sugar crash! Ro: Ahahahaha! Mo: Sugar crash!
Ro: Original? Mo: Double Stuff!
Mo:OK! Ro: Is it a repeat? What is this?

Mo: Oh, it’s chocolate! Ro: I didn’t taste
a difference!

Mo: Welp, they’re pretty good! Ro: Those
are really yummy.
Ro: I got a funny joke for you. Mo: OK.

Ro: What do you call a wealthy cookie? Mo:
What? Ro: A fortune cookie!
Mo: Ohhhhh! Ro: Whaf-whaf-whaf-whaf-whaf-whaf-whaf! Mo: Nice joke… High five!
Both: Ahahahaha!

Mo: Last cookie, this one determines it all,
everything is riding on this last bite!
Mo: Here we go…

Mo: Get off my cookie, you can’t take them
both!
Mo: Cappuccino! Ro: Creme Brule!
Mo: Cookie Dough! Ro: Cookie Dough!?!
Mo: Oh my gosh, this is really good!
Mo: Dun-da-da-duh! Da-da-da-da! Ro: Doo-doo-da-doo!

Mo: Rosanna is our winner of today’s challenge
with a whopping 4-1/2 points.

Mo: You’re lucky I gave you that 1/2 point
on the pumpkin spice

Ro: Yeah… Mo did give me that 1/2 point
so… We’re kind of tied, but I just won by a hair!

Mo: She’s that much better at guessing the
flavors. Ro: Just a li… Little bit better
Ro: of a cookie flavor guesser!

Mo: Well cheers to that! Ro: Yep! Cheers,
good game!

Ro: And, thanks for suggesting this game,
it was really fun and yummy!

Ro: And if you guys play this game, please
let us know in the comments down below

Ro: what your favorite Oreo flavor is, and
if there are any games that you’d like to

Ro: see Mo and I play in the future. Let us
know in the comments as well!

Ro: And if you want to see any of the games
that we played in the past you can
Ro: click up here! Mo: Or up here!
Ro: Woo-woo-woo! We have some Vlogs!

Ro: Alright, thanks you guys for watching
and we’ll see you later, bye-bye! Mo: Bye!

Ro: Let’s try it again, ready? Mo: OK! Ro:
1, 2… I’m gonna sense where you are. Mo: OK.
Ro: 1… Like Daredevil!
Ro: 1, 2, 3 high five!
Both: ahahaha!

Mo: Reminds me of Goldeneye, slappers only!
Ro: Slappers only! Mo: Ahahaha!
